<plot>Filmmaker Deco Dawson has created an entirely fictional biography of the internationally celebrated visual artist Marcel Dzama. FILM(dzama) is motivated by the sheer magic, humour and disobedience of Marcel Dzama's work, coupled with the the stylistically obstinate themes common to dawson's work. FILM(dzama) is an attempt to rekindle the surrealist cinema made popular in the 1920's by Dali and Bunuel and Man Ray.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?194319</url></doc>
